The model inputs (xi) are passed to the hidden neurons which operate on linear combinations of the model inputs √∞ctjxi√û. w is the sigmoidal shaped basis function, and bj are the nodal weights. The number of inputs depends on the number of parameters in the model. Hidden neurons can be arranged in one or two hidden

